
=Bios=

"Enric Senabre Hidalgo works at Dimmons as PhD candidate connecting
collaborative research practices with design thinking methodologies and agile
frameworks. He’s currently Research Fellow at CECAN, University of Surrey.
Previously he was an active member of Platoniq collective, co-founder and project manager at the platform Goteo.org for civic crowdfunding."
(http://www.share.barcelona/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/SharingCities_book.pdf)

